UltraJSON is a fast and extendable JSON encoder and decoder written in pure C

Python bindings are available as the module ujson with the methods decode and encode

Preliminary benchmarks:

Python 2.6.6 (r266:84297, Aug 24 2010, 18:46:32) [MSC v.1500 32 bit (Intel)]
OS Version: 6.1.7601 Service Pack 1 Build 7601
System Type: x64-based PC
Processor: Intel(R) Core(TM)2 Quad CPU Q9550 @ 2.83GHz 2.83 GHz
Total Physical Memory: 8191 MB

Medium complex object:
ujson encode      : 13337.87247 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 2536.91811 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 2018.48022 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 7334.94063 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 3570.38929 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 3548.34254 calls/sec

Array with 256 strings:
ujson encode      : 29876.45643 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 15715.17090 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 6368.80408 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 28368.57263 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 16485.50360 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 21175.17548 calls/sec

Array with 256 doubles:
ujson encode      : 27036.24523 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 2038.96944 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 2125.68062 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 28397.83286 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 4124.02336 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 4438.07419 calls/sec

Array with 256 True values:
ujson encode      : 97009.68060 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 34350.40502 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 47137.90414 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 97990.02609 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 57930.59829 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 74977.88879 calls/sec

Array with 256 dict{string, int} pairs:
ujson encode      : 16557.46681 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 3824.94590 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 3070.86035 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 13360.29685 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 7959.36912 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 7097.08736 calls/sec

Dict with 256 arrays with 256 dict{string, int} pairs:
ujson encode      : 50.01122 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 11.64032 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 12.88172 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 35.87532 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 24.65396 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 20.86678 calls/sec

See (python/benchmark.py) for further information.

NOTE: These benchmarks are preliminary! 

